---
// Hero: 縦スクロール開始の象徴。fullbleed / 右上に parallax ornament
---

<section
  id="top"
  class="relative min-h-[100svh] overflow-hidden bg-[var(--color-bg)] flex items-center"
>
  <!-- Parallax ornament: 右上に大きな emerald リング -->
  <div
    class="parallax absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-[640px] h-[640px] rounded-full"
    style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14,128,96,0.18) 0%, rgba(14,128,96,0.04) 45%, transparent 70%);"
    data-parallax-speed="0.18"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <!-- Parallax ornament: 左下にドットグリッド -->
  <div
    class="parallax absolute -bottom-32 -left-32 w-[420px] h-[420px] opacity-[0.07]"
    style="background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(10,10,10,1) 1.4px, transparent 1.4px); background-size: 22px 22px;"
    data-parallax-speed="-0.12"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 w-full pt-32 pb-24">
    <p
      class="reveal font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.32em] text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-6"
    >
      Taruishi Digital Research Institute LLC
    </p>

    <h1
      class="reveal reveal-delay-1 font-display text-[clamp(2.6rem,7vw,5.5rem)] leading-[1.05] text-[var(--color-text)] mb-8"
    >
      AI と人の協働で、<br />
      次の<span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">技術</span>を、<br />
      次の<span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">研究</span>を。
    </h1>

    <p
      class="reveal reveal-delay-2 max-w-xl text-base sm:text-lg text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-10"
    >
      樽石デジタル技術研究所合同会社（TDRI）は、AI エージェント基盤と
      ソフトウェアエンジニアリングを軸に、次世代の働き方と価値創造の
      仕組みを研究・実装する独立系の研究所です。
    </p>

    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
      <a
        href="#mission"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-bg-ink)] text-white text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-dim)] transition-colors"
      >
        ミッションを見る
        <span aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-[var(--color-border-ink)] text-[var(--color-text)] text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[var(--color-bg-alt)] transition-colors"
      >
        お問い合わせ
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll cue -->
    <div
      class="reveal reveal-delay-5 absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]"
    >
      <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">Scroll</span>
      <span class="block w-[1px] h-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-[var(--color-text-muted)] to-transparent">
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
